>
> Welding is not possible.
> These are EGR ports to the exhaust, and if they are still the original
tubes,
> then they are threaded into the head past several fins where a tig weld
can't go.
> They may  be replaced with a 10 X 1.0 X 35 mm bolt, or the tubes can be
plugged.
